com.google.flightmap.android
Class UserPrefs

java.lang.Object
  com.google.flightmap.android.UserPrefs

public class UserPrefs
extends Object

Provides read-only access to shared user preferences.

Write access can easily be added later. It's just not needed now, so it's not here.
